Î»dropNumericPrefix(slug:String)â†’String match #slug>4 and stdlibâ‹…string.isDigit(stdlibâ‹…string.charAt(0,slug)) and stdlibâ‹…string.isDigit(stdlibâ‹…string.charAt(1,slug)) and stdlibâ‹…string.isDigit(stdlibâ‹…string.charAt(2,slug)) and stdlibâ‹…string.charAt(3,slug)="-"{
